rComments: while this is a 101 class it is NOT easy!! The topics were rushed and work and variables were not explained. You were expected to have background knowledge in physics even though it is an introductory course. Professor was not very helpful either, and the tests were heavily weighted compared to the rest of the work.

Although its "101", it's NOT easy. Topics were crammed &not explained well.  Discussion was useless & my TA confused me more. Stay on top of the material!
